2315
01:15:48,000 --> 01:15:50,000
 patnje su označeni kao duhovne sadnje

2316
01:15:50,000 --> 01:15:54,000
 kad neko ovisnikom pati duhovno

2317
01:15:54,000 --> 01:15:57,000
 kad nekom sujom pati duhovno

2318
01:15:57,000 --> 01:15:59,000
 u savjesti

2319
01:15:59,000 --> 01:16:01,000
 kad neko razbornikom pati u sebi

2320
01:16:01,000 --> 01:16:05,000
 kad neko sujicit pravilno užasno pati

2321
01:16:05,000 --> 01:16:07,000
 uzima se život

2322
01:16:08,000 --> 01:16:09,000
 to nije fizička bol

2323
01:16:09,000 --> 01:16:11,000
 to nije bolest

2324
01:16:11,000 --> 01:16:13,000
 to nije ni psihička bol i bolest

2325
01:16:13,000 --> 01:16:16,000
 to je duhovna bol i duhovna pati

2326
01:16:16,000 --> 01:16:18,000
 dakle o tome

2327
01:16:18,000 --> 01:16:22,000
 hagio asistent da mora imati treće vlastito iskustvo da je sebi pomogao

2328
01:16:22,000 --> 01:16:25,000
