2341
01:16:52,000 --> 01:16:54,000
 ovako s Isusom biti tu

2342
01:16:54,000 --> 01:16:56,000
 igrate nogom i zajedno

2343
01:16:56,000 --> 01:16:58,000
 i treće je naravno iskustvo

2344
01:16:58,000 --> 01:17:01,000
 iskustvo susreta s Isusom

2345
01:17:01,000 --> 01:17:02,000
 iskustvo susreta s pacijentima

2346
01:17:02,000 --> 01:17:04,000
 iskustvo s vlastitim bolima

2347
01:17:04,000 --> 01:17:06,000
 patnjama i da si ih

2348
01:17:06,000 --> 01:17:08,000
