2359
01:17:36,000 --> 01:17:38,000
 sabrani

2360
01:17:38,000 --> 01:17:41,000
 a ništa ne misliš šta god je ko tebe pričaj šta ga rade šta ne

2361
01:17:41,000 --> 01:17:43,000
 ti se samo na njega

2362
01:17:43,000 --> 01:17:45,000
 razgovaraš s njegom

2363
01:17:45,000 --> 01:17:47,000
 kao kad imaš nekog interesantnu osobu

2364
01:17:47,000 --> 01:17:48,000
 vi se u tramvaju autobusa

2365
01:17:48,000 --> 01:17:50,000
 ti samo s tom osobom

2366
01:17:50,000 --> 01:17:51,000
 samo nju ugladaš s njom razgovaraš

2367
01:17:52,000 --> 01:17:54,000
 i ko te nije više interesantno

2368
01:17:54,000 --> 01:17:55,000
 to je pravo

2369
01:17:55,000 --> 01:17:56,000
 tada što poštoviš Boga

2370
01:17:56,000 --> 01:17:58,000
 ti se ti rastrešen znači da ti Bog nije važe

2371
01:17:58,000 --> 01:18:00,000
