2374
01:18:05,000 --> 01:18:06,000
 to je najtežo

2375
01:18:07,000 --> 01:18:08,000
 šte se da je bit grijeha

2376
01:18:08,000 --> 01:18:09,000
 rastrešeno se

2377
01:18:09,000 --> 01:18:11,000
